videos.headline: Toney gets loose for 66-yd TD after Florida's fake punt
videos.description: Florida converts a fake punt from its own 28-yard line and on the next play, Kadarius Toney breaks tackles for a 66-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Toney gets loose for 66-yard TD after Florida’s fake punt) 2019/08/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hurricanes break out new turnover chain
videos.description: Florida fumbles the handoff, allowing Scott Patchan to recover it and wear Miami's turnover chain.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Hurricanes break out new turnover chain) 2019/08/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Florida fumbles on 2nd straight possession
videos.description: Malik Davis can't hold onto the pitch toss and Shaquille Quarterman comes up with the fumble for Miami's second turnover recovery.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Florida fumbles on 2nd straight possession) 2019/08/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Miami debuts new drip with touchdown rings
videos.description: Jarren Williams connects with Brevin Jordan for a 25-yard Hurricanes touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Miami debuts new drip with touchdown rings) 2019/08/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gators regain lead after Canes muff punt
videos.description: Jeff Thomas fumbles the punt for Miami and Florida takes advantage as Feleipe Frank throws to Lamical Perine for a touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Gators regain lead after Canes muff punt) 2019/08/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Dallas slips tackles for 50-yard TD
videos.description: DeeJay Dallas takes off for a 50-yard touchdown for the Hurricanes.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Dallas slips tackles for 50-yard TD) 2019/08/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Carter picks Franks for Canes turnover
videos.description: Feleipe Franks' pass is tipped up and intercepted by Amari Carter to set up Miami in Florida territory.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Carter picks Franks for Canes turnover) 2019/08/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Franks deep ball sets up Gators TD run
videos.description: Feleipe Franks connects with Josh Hammond for a 65-yard pass and Franks finishes off the drive with a touchdown run.

tracking.trackingName: NCF One-Play (Franks deep ball sets up Gators TD run) 2019/08/24 ESHEET

videos.headline: Gators outlast Canes in battle for Florida
videos.description: No. 8 Florida survives multiple turnovers as Feleipe Franks throws two touchdown passes and runs for another score to take down Miami 24-20.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Gators outlast Canes in battle for Florida) 2019/08/24 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: Mullen: Gators 'found a way to win'
videos.description: Dan Mullen says Florida made a lot of mistakes but it found a way to win.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Interview (Mullen: Gators 'found a way to win') 2019/8/24
